{"word":"G4818 - συλλυπέω - syllypéō - sool-loop-eh'-o - Be grieved","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συλλυπέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>syllypéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>sool-loop-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be grieved"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விசனப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to affect with grief together"},{"paragraph":"2. to grieve with oneself"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G3076 - λυπέω - lypéō - loo-peh'-o/3076\">G3076</a>; to <i>afflict jointly</i>, that is, (passively) <i>sorrow at</i> (on account of) some one: - be grieved."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G253 - ἀλυπότερος - alypóteros - al-oo-pot'-er-os/253\">G253</a>, <a href=\"#/G3076 - λυπέω - lypéō - loo-peh'-o/3076\">G3076</a>, <a href=\"#/G3077 - λύπη - lýpē - loo'-pay/3077\">G3077</a>, <a href=\"#/G4036 - περίλυπος - perílypos - per-il'-oo-pos/4036\">G4036</a>, <a href=\"#/G4818 - συλλυπέω - syllypéō - sool-loop-eh'-o/4818\">G4818</a>"}]}